<div class="container homepage">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <h2 class="login-title">Login</h2>
        <form class="login-form">
            <div class="form-group mb-2">
                <label class="sr-only" for="email-login">Email:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control-plaintext" id="email-login" placeholder="email@example.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="sr-only" for="password-login">Password:</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password-login" placeholder="Password" required>
            </div>
            <button class="btn btn-primary mb-2" type="submit" id="loginBtn" title="Login">Login</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary mb-2" id="showSignup" title="Signup">Signup!</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div id="secondCol" class="col">
        <h4 id="secondCol-title">Wecome to Budgetek!</h4>
        <p id="secondCol-info">Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aspernatur nisi ex, magnam, alias perferendis accusantium iure voluptatem amet, ad et inventore blanditiis dolorum natus recusandae culpa neque atque! Inventore, dolore.</p>
    </div>
  <form id="signUpDisplay" class="signup-form">
    <h2>Please signup to start budgeting today!</h2>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label class="font-weight-bold" for="username-signup">Username:</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username-signup" required>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label class="font-weight-bold" for="email-signup">Email:</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="email-signup" required>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label class="font-weight-bold" for="password-signup">Password:</label>
      <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password-signup" required>
    </div>
      <button class="btn btn-success" id="signupBtn" type="submit" title="Sign me in">Sign Me Up</button>
  </form>
</div>

<script src="/javascript/login.js"></script>